      • getServerList

        public CompletableFuture<Vector<InetSocketAddress>> getServerList(MasterServerType type,
                                                                  MasterServerRegion region,
                                                                  MasterServerFilter filter,
                                                                  TriConsumer<InetSocketAddress,InetSocketAddress,Throwable> callback)

        Retrieves a list of servers from the Steam Master Server.

        Parameters:
        type - A MasterServerType to indicate which type of servers the master server should return
        region - A MasterServerRegion value that specifies which server region the master server should return
        filter - A MasterServerFilter representing a set of filters to be used by the query
        callback - A TriConsumer that will be invoked repeatedly for partial response
        Returns:
        A CompletableFuture containing a Vector of InetSocketAddress.
        See Also:
        getServerList(MasterServerType, MasterServerRegion, MasterServerFilter)
